snippet.title: Lucky Tower Ultimate - Early Access Out now!
snippet.description:
Out now! Grab it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1700270/Lucky_Tower_Ultimate

Studio Seufz and AMC Games present: LUCKY TOWER ULTIMATE. 

Escape from a dangerous tower where everything can be a weapon. Lucky Tower Ultimate is a slapstick, roguelike adventure that looks like a cartoon and feels like a joke. Slashy slashy!

Join the Lucky Tower Discord community: https://discord.gg/nGkr4kqV68
